==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Copartnership
<hw>Co*part"ner*ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state of
being a copartner or of having a joint interest in any matter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A partnership or firm; <as>as, A</as>. and B. have
this day formed a <xex>copartnership</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Copartnery</ent>⟦br⟧
